OL,3,CThe Houthis, Iran's allies, threaten
OL,4,Canother trade route to Europe
OL,6,FIran's allies, the Houthis in Yemen,
OL,7,Fare threatening to close a major trade
OL,8,Froute between Europe and Asia,
OL,9,Faccording to intelligence sources in
OL,10,Fthe region.
OL,12,FITV News has been told there is real
OL,13,Fconcern that an expansion of the war
OL,14,Fwill see the Houthis engage and
OL,15,Fdisrupt shipping through Bab el-
OL,16,FMandeb, which lies between Yemen and
OL,17,FDjibouti.
OL,19,FIt is the direct route to the Suez
OL,20,FCanal and the Mediterranean and is
OL,21,FEurope's primary trade link with Asia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
