CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773216518
OL,3,CThe Houthis, Iran's allies, threaten
OL,4,Canother trade route to Europe
OL,6,FSources wouldn't explicitly lay out
OL,7,Fwhat escalation looked like, but
OL,8,Findicated the Houthis were alert to
OL,9,Fother countries acting against Iran.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAny disruption of traffic would have a
OL,17,Fnear-immediate impact on the
OL,18,Favailability and cost of imports such
OL,19,Fas electronics, household goods,
OL,20,Fclothing, and toys, among other things.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
