CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773216518
OL,3,CThe Houthis, Iran's allies, threaten
OL,4,Canother trade route to Europe
OL,6,FWhat's more, the strait provides a
OL,7,Froute for oil and liquefied natural
OL,8,Fgas to Europe.
OL,10,FAlready, oil prices have shot up since
OL,11,Fthe start of the war one week ago as a
OL,12,Fresult of the impact of a reduction in
OL,13,Ftraffic through the other critical
OL,14,Fwaterway, the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,16,FLast week, Abdul Malil al-Houthi, the
OL,17,FHouthi leader, said his group was
OL,18,Fready "to move militarily if
OL,19,Fdevelopments require it", warning "our
OL,20,Fhands are on the trigger whenever
OL,21,Fdevelopments require it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
