FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773216518
OL,3,CThe Houthis, Iran's allies, threaten
OL,4,Canother trade route to Europe
OL,6,FWith the oil price now more than $100
OL,7,Fa barrel - a four-year high - US
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump has threatened
OL,9,FIran with "death, fire and fury" if it
OL,10,Ffurther blocks the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,11,Fone of two vital trade routes in the
OL,12,FMiddle East.
OL,14,FHe said the country would be hit 20
OL,15,Ftimes harder than it's already been
OL,16,Fhit should there be a further
OL,17,Ftightening on passage through the
OL,18,Fwaterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
