OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773216518
OL,3,CThe Houthis, Iran's allies, threaten
OL,4,Canother trade route to Europe
OL,6,FIran's Republican Guard says if the
OL,7,Fattacks continue, not even a litre of
OL,8,Foil will be allowed through.
OL,10,FAlready, there's been an estimated 70
OL,11,Fto 80% drop in tanker traffic through
OL,12,Fthe Strait, which normally is the
OL,13,Froute for 20% of the world's oil
OL,14,Fsupply.
OL,16,FAfter October 7, the Houthis launched
OL,17,Fattacks on shipping in the Red Sea,
OL,18,Fwhich forced huge diversions for
OL,19,Ftraffic, resulting in triple the cost
OL,20,Fof freight rates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
